  <h1>15+ Tutorial Dasar CSS</h1>

  <div class="container">

    <div class="card">
      <h3>1. background-color</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Memberi warna latar elemen.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>background-color: lightblue;</code></p>
      <div class="example bg-example">Warna latar belakang</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>2. color</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Mengubah warna teks.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>color: red;</code></p>
      <div class="example color-example">Teks berwarna merah</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>3. padding</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Menambah jarak isi ke pinggir elemen.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>padding: 20px;</code></p>
      <div class="example padding-example">Dengan padding</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>4. margin</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Memberi jarak antar elemen.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>margin: 20px 0;</code></p>
      <div class="example margin-example">Dengan margin</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>5. border</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Menambahkan garis tepi.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>border: 2px solid green;</code></p>
      <div class="example border-example">Dengan border</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>6. border-radius</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Membulatkan sudut elemen.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>border-radius: 20px;</code></p>
      <div class="example radius-example">Sudut membulat</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>7. box-shadow</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Memberi bayangan.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);</code></p>
      <div class="example shadow-example">Dengan bayangan</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>8. text-align</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Mengatur posisi teks.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>text-align: right;</code></p>
      <div class="example text-align-example">Teks kanan</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>9. font-family</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Mengubah jenis huruf.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>font-family: 'Courier New';</code></p>
      <div class="example font-example">Font Courier</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>10. width</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Mengatur lebar elemen.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>width: 100px;</code></p>
      <div class="example width-example">Lebar 100px</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>11. display</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Tipe tampilan elemen (block, inline, dll).</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>display: inline-block;</code></p>
      <div class="example display-example">Inline Block</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>12. position</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Menentukan posisi elemen.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>position: relative; top: 10px;</code></p>
      <div class="example position-example">Posisi relatif</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>13. :hover</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Efek saat kursor diarahkan.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>:hover { background-color: yellow; }</code></p>
      <div class="example hover-example">Arahkan mouse ke sini</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>14. flex</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Mengatur layout fleksibel.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>display: flex;</code></p>
      <div class="example flex-example">
        <div class="flex-item">1</div>
        <div class="flex-item">2</div>
        <div class="flex-item">3</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>15. box-sizing</h3>
      <p><b>Fungsi:</b> Menghitung padding dan border dalam width.</p>
      <p><b>CSS:</b> <code>box-sizing: border-box;</code></p>
      <div class="example" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid #aaa; width: 150px; padding: 10px;">
        Contoh box-sizing
      </div>
